race.description: Become A Brc Member Mdn Hcp
race.comment: NOTTINGTON PRINCE (1) has finished runner-up at the past couple and looks to be on the doorstep of a maiden victory. Melbourne Cup-winning hoop Dolan sticks in the saddle and can go one better against this line-up. DIALIDAE (6) has been just behind the placegetters in both outings this campaign and is drawn to get a cosy run in transit from the inside alley. Should be hitting the line with gusto. KING COBAMA (2) was a touch plain last time out but go on the close-up second on debut. Capable of a better showing. OUR BRAVE LINI (11) wasn't disgraced when facing the starter for the first time and can feature with natural improvement. JUSTA BARTY (8) hails from an astute stable and any market confidence must be noted.
